{"title":"Estenosis aórtica-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Estenosis aórtica-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Estenosis\\Naórtica","guid":"xl2Y5rw8-JsjWV2VhuCYKw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"_t1Uay0idYX3jpFalgdyrQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición:","guid":"dLNGDFguQtq_TosN99X-3Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Enfermedad valvular → Estrechamiento válvula aórtica","guid":"ZGu1NR1x6Su79UMoIt8rNg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Obstrucción salida VI → Aorta","guid":"RolwjkGPYdHnlfc7sO5Spg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• Sobrecarga crónica VI → Insuficiencia ventricular izquierda (IVI) potencial","guid":"TH0yJxiqKNzPGm17RuMYVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Clínica:","guid":"tQ-EbTEKL--CLtX5Rwektw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Fase asintomática prolongada","guid":"bMs6nkKpkWuK-3Gz_YSlAg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Síntomas al inicio: Disnea de esfuerzo, angina pectoris, síncope","guid":"dBkzPt0uLik2DBmtSo0KcQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Auscultación: Soplo sistólico áspero, crescendo-decrescendo → Irradiación hacia carótidas","guid":"ogk-6PgMFFM-gXezT-o5pQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"• Pulsos carotídeos disminuidos, retardo de ascenso","guid":"Lyi9ztLHRjzJeVHjKmM7cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"L9I8-LV1B3MeCL2Z0c74Cg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Estandar: Ecocardiografía → No invasiva","guid":"rlzmI6zlHhOd_rJRXfbkoQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Seguimiento conservador → EA leve asintomática","guid":"zEwjP-GxeD2_xmgb2RFyxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"XoPkgJPC_-h5PrfJSaYkDQ","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• EA grave/sintomática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Reemplazo valvular aórtico (RVA) → Quirúrgico o Transcatéter (TAVR) en alto riesgo quirúrgico","guid":"AT_LA5Nc26dOAxFQnkpOlg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Manejo médico comorbilidades: HTA","guid":"I4S-Z0z2_4CWz2yF17E3Qw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"-aEdZ-0PTuQIRP0FelZ0Ug","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Alto riesgo de fallo cardíaco agudo","guid":"s3_H7zZkv_dnSa0ZV7o8uA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Shock cardiogénico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Intervenciones críticas (UCI) → RVA urgente/TAVR","guid":"6k258977-sjIhTZkWoSmMw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"eBvBTzdVmmU8p4TTSw0JCA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Prevalencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Enfermedad valvular más común en países industrializados (1)","guid":"YhpfIr_S2xAzoy6W9u4Iyg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• ↑ prevalencia con la edad","guid":"n9bd1S1X5CnTPndRSYPcig","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• 12,4% en ≥ 75 años (1)","guid":"OIu1Os1g9xfcvPqsXMeBUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"• Asociaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Frecuentemente asociada con insuficiencia aórtica (1)","guid":"q72OAM7JFHMb_8qkFf1W-g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Etiología","guid":"gT7YyYpGQhHKqKaymymXlw","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Esclerosis\\Nvalvular aórtica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Calcificación y fibrosis de las valvas aórticas (2)","guid":"WTmdgsBHnSMXVE1oJUagng","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Causa más común de EA","guid":"VJw5kuZL-VSgiK0ZQZHQaA","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"• ↑ tasa con la edad: 35% en 75–85 años (3)","guid":"rfcA3vyTea5l_2jPiG3lag","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"• Fisiopatología similar a aterosclerosis (2)","guid":"qjViSOBBviH9VoUBj0kBHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"29","text":"• Válvula aórtica bicúspide\\N(VAB):","guid":"cMVFSGMP8nSgYvcx5oZ5wQ","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Fusión de dos de las tres valvas en útero (2)","guid":"rBN-G4XkynQem_YwtgiRag","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• Malformación congénita más común → Afecta predominantemente a varones (3:1) (4)","guid":"JDr-HJx2yKjZTQ7HK4KUpw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"• Predispone a calcificación distrófica y degeneración","guid":"s8LfXu7xl7xm142EF8ilFQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"• Síntomas de EA aparecen más temprano que en calcificación valvular normal (2, 4)","guid":"LErdcWVnA68PSUG6nMRgjQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"• Estenosis congénita rara → Válvula unicúspide o bicúspide (3)","guid":"u8ELH39EGVPaJP-nA_G8EA","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"29","text":"• Fiebre\\Nreumática:","guid":"IWb-FIzaPZDRcCSydJB5GQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Causa rara en países de altos ingresos → Uso consistente de antibióticos para faringitis estreptocócica (3)","guid":"tFenQ2Jx9sPnECVdxfOgyw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Causa significativa en países de bajos ingresos → Menor acceso a antibióticos (3)","guid":"S8Yjipw6VCNpjcXe7cADLg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"• Estenosis por fusión comisural (3)","guid":"Gnl8IaGhe1nnV0FWaRrDTg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"• Progresión:","guid":"uT9UhAW55YbR_Zzf8zvUSA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Esclerosis aórtica → Sin EA en etapas iniciales","guid":"F2scT_IYxKjCvDhXoZE2Iw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Progresión a EA con obstrucción del tracto de salida del VI (5)","guid":"bTHQaRp4IkvK-HlEDr8d5w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"3xsbGL13LMx5KoWajkfHPw","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Estrechez de la válvula aórtica en sístole →\\NObstrucción del flujo sanguíneo desde VI →\\N↑ presión en VI → Hipertrofia concéntrica del VI, \\Nlo que conlleva:","guid":"OIHeF3yX-Vvt1-RASJ-Nlw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• ↑ demanda de oxígeno del VI","guid":"QLqHii8fB3Jhb81vFTEbww","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• Llenado ventricular alterado en diástole → Insuficiencia cardíaca izquierda (ICI)","guid":"tWZ4epQnB3XxU_vQhyhTPg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"• ↓ reserva de flujo coronario","guid":"z_1bZUhtrOpTTmZf3Ww3EA","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"• Compensación inicial:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Gasto cardíaco (GC) mantenido inicialmente (ver mecanismos de compensación en “Insuficiencia cardíaca congestiva”)","guid":"9xHFY7XdktGY9ZLHrDlMGQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"• Descompensación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• ↓ distensibilidad del VI → ↓ GC → Regurgitación hacia venas pulmonares y capilares →\\N↑ postcarga (presión pulmonar) sobre corazón derecho → Insuficiencia cardíaca derecha (ICD)","guid":"6YMeRhVxY-rTgFAsM_bFUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Clínica ","guid":"uKzFM_zjjSUVy-N48I2iJQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Asintomática durante años en casos leves/moderados","guid":"UWYAi-pxLQ9r8QthYK5xWA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Síntomas en EA grave → Reposo o esfuerzo","guid":"VpNkBDlHwhQZYAG4TqDVEQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Signos y\\Nsíntomas:","guid":"jU7OIwm_QavjlTe70LG3JA","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Disnea (típicamente de esfuerzo)","guid":"a8PJ9mIi4fBCE1gCfdhSDg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Angina pectoris","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Mareos y síncope","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Infantes: sibilancias, dificultad para alimentarse","guid":"UFHFdTsxWA24JEbQVz2dlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"57","text":"Examen\\Nfísico:","guid":"7NP4B7JJ8mnElhslVgoCjQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Amplitud de presión arterial baja, ↓ presión de pulso","guid":"E3Mr76oODGJdq9v9reGjhQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Pulso débil y retrasado (pulsus parvus et tardus) (2)","guid":"ejwWCifgPUg0Ci39OikZNQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"• Frémito sistólico palpable sobre bifurcación de carótidas y aorta (2)","guid":"vYz6YnMFEeyzXJXTOXDxxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"57","text":"Auscultación:","guid":"ekej8w0M_8RZiraEmfFRDQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Soplo sistólico de eyección en crescendo-decrescendo (forma de diamante),\\Ntardío, irradiado bilateralmente a carótidas","guid":"AjsLnwiEyAALQ7tTXx7l4w","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Mejor auscultación: 2° espacio intercostal derecho","guid":"j40E99u8i7BBsZTO9NhXRw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• ↓ intensidad con maniobra de handgrip","guid":"1OSnSb57WjEVeh2i6-WMhQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"• Maniobras de Valsalva y ponerse de pie ↓ o sin cambios en intensidad\\N(diferencia con miocardiopatía hipertrófica)","guid":"w53Ow__-r6rMDLM2hKC98A","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"• S2 suave","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"69","text":"• S4 mejor audible en el ápex","guid":"HMUiTIL22-pBKBQlWzqxkw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"69","text":"• Chasquido de eyección sistólico temprano","guid":"GNlLK_PtZtVLQq3Ij8HSgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"57","text":"Mnemotecnia: SAD → Síncope, Angina, Disnea","guid":"eekuldIhXmcWO6fGa_p64A","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación\\NSistema AHA/ACC","guid":"dAqZSGRWcAfeOndEqqM1Eg","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Propósito: Monitorizar la progresión de la enfermedad y determinar la necesidad de intervención","guid":"eAchfuHiRV-PKTEfOd29AA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Basada en: Criterios ecocardiográficos de anatomía y hemodinámica valvular","guid":"qco4z7xJpgh_qQz5KHntJw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"Factores\\Nclave:","guid":"OiGBMiJX2GiNJPCue14VJQ","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Área valvular aórtica (AVA): Medida del área de apertura de la válvula aórtica en sístole\\N→ Factor principal para evaluar la gravedad de EA","guid":"_qWct9wSdxwyZm-X4cDcUQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"• Gradiente de presión aórtica media: Diferencia de presión entre VI y aorta ascendente durante la sístole","guid":"9k9ZFLaxgtYSgUq4NFygiA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"• Estenosis valvular → ↑ gradiente debido a limitación en ↑ presión aórtica y ↑ presión VI","guid":"WfzCnrZp0fcCBscZWTk0Zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"Clasificación\\NAHA/ACC de la EA","guid":"96VOY7V50ckKUoLzHp5KIw","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• EA leve a\\Nmoderada:","guid":"iGbQV91Jj-VveXU3dCpveQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Estadio A: Riesgo de EA","guid":"MEh0kLEmS_og3qzclXZoyQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• Estadio B:\\NEA progresiva","guid":"0VJ9LHOW-TCdTBrGv3-e4Q","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Leve: AVA 1.5–2.9 cm²","guid":"Ci3oUmY722CJj11YTxLEPg","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Gradiente de presión: 10–19 mm Hg","guid":"go8DzvBoviXmJRMCZfR8HQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"• Moderada: AVA 1.0–1.4 cm²","guid":"Kl3JbxrpFBEPsdqHws0p0g","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Gradiente de presión: 20–39 mm Hg","guid":"TMuQrrq0u4dBbMqX9jzSHQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"85","text":"• EA grave:","guid":"S9IkZVMCvw_Zr6awUuWXKQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Estadio C1: EA grave asintomática con FEVI normal","guid":"JcjcwmaI4p45X02FJ_F8SQ","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• Estadio C2: EA grave asintomática con disfunción del VI (FEVI < 50%)","guid":"x3aaJ13jqCjux-BijeAI7g","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"• Estadio D: EA grave sintomática","guid":"jVIFNF_qWBZvBRITeOQxrA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"0gMcNKcC-LgQ18FKkXmBGQ","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación\\NInicial","guid":"73-f-Xrj8Q92xyIzodFFkQ","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Ecocardiografía (9)","guid":"iV3zbL3ZQ4MJxLnekp4GeA","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Indicación: Evaluación de la estructura, función y severidad de la válvula aórtica, VI y otras válvulas cardíacas","guid":"yCDd7gPZZj8oBn9zIt0SFA","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• TTE (ecocardiografía transtorácica): Prueba primaria recomendada y\\Nestándar no invasivo para confirmar diagnóstico y determinar severidad de EA","guid":"hPc8dvMFL7c2dIu-2TiRWA","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"• TEE (ecocardiografía transesofágica): Modalidad de segunda línea\\Npara confirmar hallazgos de TTE o planificación quirúrgica (13)","guid":"TRrLPXBZa_ovHfv9cFsk6g","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"Hallazgos\\Nde soporte:","guid":"i4GuLhc9-IY92renEIJ0GQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Calcificación y estrechamiento de la válvula aórtica","guid":"7_6quGYfayf2P4q9xDzT_g","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"• ↑ Gradiente de presión aórtica media y velocidad transvalvular","guid":"xPTyhP2gCz1w7VELjQNqwA","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"• Signos de remodelado cardíaco → Hipertrofia concéntrica","guid":"u_p3rsBfWqeBpenkujQuyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"98","text":"Otras pruebas","guid":"iexGokgQWkeapeDu9Rp0Rg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"• ECG (2,3)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Signos de hipertrofia ventricular izquierda (HVI) → Índice Sokolow-Lyon positivo","guid":"vRIe0xMj0YXVAWIBikyFkg","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Anomalías inespecíficas del ST-segmento y onda T","guid":"I24fRFwfb2LOpDNiL5vLHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"107","text":"• Radiografía de\\Ntórax (2,3)","guid":"nYn0VoJOHQ8lDR56ejgvSA","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Evaluación para edema pulmonar u otras causas de disnea","guid":"igVDzMjDj3N0YQuHTx5sIg","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"• Calcificaciones visibles en válvula aórtica → Indicador de enfermedad grave","guid":"07gFjcU4FNwSjvk6PXD-bA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"• Estrechamiento del espacio retrocardíaco\\N(vista lateral)","guid":"0JR8U4-ZmfmzA2XSZSJJNg","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"111","text":"• Signos de remodelado cardíaco y falla cardíaca asociada:\\NHVI, congestión pulmonar, dilatación postestenótica de la aorta","guid":"RgzoXNBt4_Xfy7OghoYCzg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación\\NAdicional","guid":"0GcnlhJnsqjHfwzvGpNdMA","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Cateterismo\\Ncardíaco (9)","guid":"ISiyDuiE5Hg1A3-Ew8TlTA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Prueba diagnóstica precisa para evaluar área valvular aórtica, GC y gradiente de presión aórtica media","guid":"Ze_ulZECazT_C-XoNAe53g","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• No indicado de forma rutinaria","guid":"biGFmjzaPULMF-qjfGhfOA","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"• Considerar en pacientes sintomáticos con pruebas no invasivas inconclusas o discrepancia entre síntomas y pruebas (18)","guid":"Gwh5n_H8zNTc_aoVEHrCdQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"• Hallazgos similares a los de la ecocardiografía","guid":"r1fWVcViQ8RkySLXOndX9A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico Diferencial de\\NEstenosis Aórtica (EA)","guid":"89iujMbuDURdizuN3Zmgpw","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• Valvulopatías:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"• Ver “Enfermedades valvulares cardíacas” para visión general de otras valvulopatías.","guid":"KA4inEoOjY2RJZ_pZp5qcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"• Síncope:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Ver “Diagnóstico diferencial de síncope” y “Causas de síncope”.","guid":"Ghgy9ebQcvEcXUkg1v91XQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"• Dolor torácico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Ver “Diagnóstico diferencial de dolor torácico”.","guid":"KSzeGiWqSvrQGVEdyb1yxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"• Disnea:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• Ver “Diagnóstico diferencial de disnea”.","guid":"tPPcnlUPvn7BBQt5xZoWNw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento de la\\NEstenosis Aórtica (EA)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Enfoque (9):","guid":"8fFvfBMUtymbPmnnTwS2hQ","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"• EA sintomática y/o grave: Indicación para reemplazo o reparación valvular aórtica","guid":"yL8Ro6s03WoSywZtyLTnMA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"• EA asintomática o leve-moderada: Tratamiento conservador; considerar reemplazo temprano en algunos pacientes (20)","guid":"pYsn86s9IF3Uqk5nZ2dtIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"Todos los\\Npacientes:","guid":"fFXItP3_Op1IVMXbwCTKPA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• Cuidado de soporte: Manejo de comorbilidades (HTA, DM), seguimiento con ecocardiografía seriada, profilaxis de EI para pacientes en riesgo.","guid":"F9i5y2LpiSjrn3Nr4w50rA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"• Manejo de complicaciones críticas (e.g., IC aguda) → Cuidados intensivos y tratamiento quirúrgico urgente.","guid":"W9boFJoJ6QtTE1QUKJLwig","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"0","text":"Reemplazo/Reparación\\Nvalvular aórtica (AVR) (9)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"CfBcKbBS5V_P3uIwMucEng","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Pacientes sintomáticos con EA grave de alto gradiente","guid":"fg0-f4uAjPWYBnVPyiwWrw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Pacientes asintomáticos\\Ncon EA grave y:","guid":"3C4CXTBD3JmRHozcher6oA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• FEVI significativamente ↓","guid":"AJSJZSLbkpUg0TFD0J9Lkw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"• Cirugía cardíaca por otras indicaciones","guid":"bXz8uHzCFGYDR_OR28sxMg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"138","text":"Procedimiento:","guid":"kLNYSSueXNIA-YB2yZX4Tw","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Reemplazo quirúrgico de\\Nválvula aórtica (SAVR):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Edad < 65 años","guid":"DqXhPVPQRSPi06yEfcwGoQ","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"• Expectativa de vida > 20 años","guid":"VDrgeNKWR5nKI3vBUuI8iQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"• Riesgo quirúrgico bajo a moderado","guid":"_-908Ym_ooFivaZ77cR99w","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"• Reemplazo valvular\\Ntranscatéter (TAVR):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Edad > 80 años","guid":"so0CX1S-TpGafwvMlbdsDg","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"• Expectativa de vida < 10 años","guid":"2c5CON1tOv-5z17e9NRLYA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"• Alto riesgo quirúrgico o prohibitivo y supervivencia > 12 meses (9)","guid":"ZlHsTd0e2yucoYnq9gP2jA","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"144","text":"• Valvuloplastía percutánea\\Ncon balón (9):","guid":"9Cwbir2fo0WJXwvKvntYVA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Útil en niños, adolescentes y adultos jóvenes","guid":"bU20hXA6DlkhjiHmgYtCJQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Rol limitado en pacientes mayores","guid":"l7uCms6mrRkOuAtp1XCwHA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"138","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"68EKyMCcw4BnoX_wWi1Cww","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Shock cardiogénico","guid":"oPxx39XA3oMjCtFOKr-eJQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Insuficiencia cardíaca aguda (IC aguda)","guid":"54lDjkW0Taf50Ttf4zsIUg","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Fibrilación auricular con respuesta ventricular rápida (RVR)","guid":"GrCJb6d1WQSRXivz7jOZIg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Pacientes asintomáticos:","guid":"NDs7rNcJXor9ynPhOmlU0g","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Tasa de mortalidad < 1% por año (24)","guid":"nH4WEHD2VrSAMdn_nLgByw","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"• Pacientes\\Nsintomáticos:","guid":"d2Lem5iVupC5nyC6LIKJXg","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• Tasa de mortalidad en los primeros 2 años > 50% si no se trata (39)","guid":"D2Wp83RkspxuJI8ks2dBQw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• Pronóstico peor en IC, seguido de síncope y angina pectoris (40)","guid":"ReI6CRUeYJrdpRmC2lRMLA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":165,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Estenosis aórtica-2024","id":"map_744","resolved_references":[]}